One thing worthy of mentioning is the fact that many sysops are
insisting that all messages be written in english. At the very same
time, the very same sysops are using a swedish localization..no names..


The current version is 2.x and it's totally different in operation. You
will need to scrap 1.x and install 2.x before the end of this month.
I might finish the work with 3.x before the end of the month, see below
how to get either version easiest.

The major differences between 1.x and 2.x:
