for amiga, pc, consoles and whatever.

These should all be part of a single executable, but I may decide to
release them as separate programs instead if time is short, especially
DC_Speed since it has to be running for a month to be useful.



To get the latest release, the easiest way is to call my board and logon as
"DreamChart" with pw "DC", this account has enough access to get the latest
release and information. This account can also be used to leave statfiles
and feedback.

